highlights.text: “Nice To Each Other” by Olivia Dean has been on Viral Songs United Kingdom the longest, at 81 days straight.
Hayley Williams has the most spots on Viral Songs United Kingdom. “Mirtazapine” is the highest at #36.
“No Lie” by Harry T is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs United Kingdom, up 19 spots at #47.
“Flowers” by Born On Road and Brodie is the highest new entry on Viral Songs United Kingdom at #14.
